Class JsonKeysetReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.crypto.tink.JsonKeysetReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeysetReader
    public final class JsonKeysetReader
extends Object
implements KeysetReader
    A KeysetReader that can read from source source cleartext or encrypted keysets in proto JSON format.

    1.0.0
